author: Min Zeng
title: U.S. Government Debt Set for Quarterly Gain
text:
U.S. government bonds pulled back Wednesday after a two-day price gain, but they are still headed for a rally for the quarter, beating both U.S. stocks and corporate bonds sold by lower-rated companies.
